org.pepstock.charba.client.intl

Enum Script

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Script>
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.intl.Script
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Script>, Key, IsLocaleItem

    public enum Script
extends Enum<Script>
implements IsLocaleItem
    Enumerates the standard codes for script identification which can be used to create and manage locale.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
